### üîÑ Content Maintenance & Governance
- Who writes and approves content?
- How often is content reviewed or updated?
- Is there a versioning or revision history system?

### üîç SEO or External Strategy (if applicable)
- Will content appear in public-facing areas (blogs, landing pages)?
- Are keywords, metadata, or schema markup required?
